high_descs: Turn left then right and face the table to your right.
Take the knife off of the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the counter with the tomato on your right.
Slice the tomato on the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge, place the knife inside then close it.
Turn left and face the counter with the tomato on your left.
Take a tomato slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn right and face the pan on the stove on your left.
Place the tomato slice in the pan on the stove in front of you.
Take the pan from the stove in front of you.
Turn left and face the fridge on your left.
Place the pan inside of the fridge then close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a tomato slice on a pan in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk around to face the left side of the white table.
Pick up the knife on the white table.
Turn right and step forward to face the tomato on the end of the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the end of the counter.
Pick up a tomato slice on the end of the counter.
Take a step to the right to face the stove.
Place the tomato on the front left pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan with the tomato slice on the stove.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Place the pan with a tomato slice in it in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To place a tomato slice in a pan plus move them to the fridge.

high_descs: go to the end of the white table
pick up the knife from the table
take the knife to the counter
slice the tomato
take the knife to the fridge
put the knife in the fridge
go back to the counter with the tomato
pick up a tomato slice
take the slice to the stove
put the slice in the pan on the stove on the left
pick up the pan
take the pan to the fridge
put the pan in the fridge
anns.task_desc: cut a tomato, put a slice in a pan in the fridge
